To Work loacly:
1. Start Redis server:
a. open ubuntu 18.04 LTS
b. type - sudo service redis-server start
c. type sudo password

2. open a terminal for each process:
a. main.py (the web process in Heroku)
b. worker.py (type in terminal python worker.py)
c. clock.py (type in terminal python clock.py)




DB mapping:
prices
wallets - (user), miners
miners - (wallet)

users - wallets, posts, comments, messages

posts - (user), comments
comments - (user), (post)
messages - (user)

activity_log - What events to log?: registration, login, message sent, new post posted, new comment posted
transactions